This is a bash script to install slimmed Ubuntu LTS 24.04

Fully netinstall.
No snap.
No sudo.
No gpt.
No network-manager.
Just base system + xorg + choosen wm.
Installation is processed textually by asking relevant questions.

Usage:
  Boot from any GNU/Linux LiveCD, download this script and run as root:
# wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/vallbsd/ubslim/refs/heads/main/ubslim.sh
# bash ubslim.sh
